  <summary date="2023-04-11T12:20:54Z" status="Introduced in House">Stop Trying to Obsessively Vilify Energy Act or the STOVE Act

This bill prohibits federal agencies from promulgating rules or guidances that restrict or ban the use and purchase of gas-powered stoves, cooktops, ranges, or ovens in the United States.</summary>
